OL,3,CTfL to ban non-folding e-bikes
OL,5,FAll non-folding e-bikes will be banned
OL,6,Fon London Tube and rail services from
OL,7,Fthe end of the month to ensure the
OL,8,Fsafety of customers and staff, it has
OL,9,Fbeen announced.
OL,11,FTransport for London (TfL) said it has
OL,12,Fbeen working with the London Fire
OL,13,FBrigade and other partners to carry
OL,14,Fout a comprehensive review of the
OL,15,Fsafety of e-bikes and their
OL,16,Fsuitability for carriage on the
OL,17,Ftransport network.
OL,19,FThe train drivers union Aslef welcomed
OL,20,Fthe move after pressing for a ban on
OL,21,Fsafety grounds.
