OL,3,CTfL to ban non-folding e-bikes
OL,5,FAslef issued its safety warning after
OL,6,Fan e-bike caught fire on a platform at
OL,7,FRayners Lane Tube station in north-
OL,8,Fwest London last month.JThe fire was
OL,9,Fput out by crews from London Fire
OL,10,FBrigade.
OL,12,FMayor of London Sir Sadiq Khan said:
OL,13,F"The safety of Londoners is my top
OL,14,Fpriority and, while most e-bikes are
OL,15,Fsafe, there have been a small number
OL,16,Fof incidents where non-foldable e-
OL,17,Fbikes have caught fire on the
OL,18,Ftransport system, which have caused me
OL,19,Fgreat concern.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/8
