OL,3,CTfL to ban non-folding e-bikes
OL,5,F"This is why, following a
OL,6,Fcomprehensive review of the safety of
OL,7,Fe-bikes, TfL is banning all non-
OL,8,Ffolding e-bikes on Tube and rail
OL,9,Fservices. I have asked TfL to continue
OL,10,Fto work with Government and partners
OL,11,Fto improve e-bike safety as we build a
OL,12,Fsafer London for everyone."
OL,14,FTfL said in a statement: "While the
OL,15,Fmajority of e-bikes are safe, there
OL,16,Fhave been a small number of incidents
OL,17,Fwhere non-foldable e-bikes have caught
OL,18,Ffire on the transport system in London.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/8
