OL,3,CTfL to ban non-folding e-bikes
OL,5,F"It will reduce the risk of a serious
OL,6,Faccident, and the dangers caused by
OL,7,Flarge numbers of unfolded e-bikes
OL,8,Fblocking exits in emergencies.
OL,10,F"We are pleased that TfL have listened
OL,11,Fto our concerns and acted on them."
OL,13,FTfL said it is the first transport
OL,14,Foperator in the UK to enforce such a
OL,15,Fban.JLondon Fire Brigade have also
OL,16,Fwelcomed the move.
