OL,3,CTfL to ban non-folding e-bikes
OL,5,F"When these fires occur, they can be
OL,6,Fsudden, incredibly ferocious and
OL,7,Fproduce smoke that is extremely toxic."
OL,9,FHowever, some do not believe the ban
OL,10,Fgoes far enough.
OL,12,FTransport Salaried Staffs Association
OL,13,Fgeneral secretary Maryam Eslamdoust
OL,14,Fsaid: "Folding e-bikes may be smaller,
OL,15,Fbut they still use the same lithium-
OL,16,Fion batteries, and they're just as
OL,17,Fcapable of catching fire or exploding.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/8
